{"tid":2292100,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"黃廠賣口罩遭黨媒批鬥違國安法 兩門市及網頁急停運","createTime":"2020-11-19T08:45:00.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-19T19:14:00.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"3bab2040a400e336005fc4d6b7d5111806549604","tid":2292100,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-19T08:45:00.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201118/ST5ZD2EKGFCVLNKZMWNFAL3GYU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201118%2FST5ZD2EKGFCVLNKZMWNFAL3GYU%2F&d=kK8wO%2BHHGyY98lbbYtfopRnxOJLX742lx1SCoot1iYY%3D&h=b7594a28\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201118%2FST5ZD2EKGFCVLNKZMWNFAL3GYU%2F&h=021ee0dd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201118/ST5ZD2EKGFCVLNKZMWNFAL3GYU/</a><br />\n<br />\n黃廠賣口罩遭黨媒批鬥違國安法 兩門市及網頁急停運<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/JWuK6CILJVJ82YXYZlnSw56iyco=/1950x1097/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/4WOJRFUEURCHBNALEV225YFMZ4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FJWuK6CILJVJ82YXYZlnSw56iyco%3D%2F1950x1097%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F4WOJRFUEURCHBNALEV225YFMZ4.jpg&h=b75501df&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n黃廠遭黨媒批鬥後，今宣佈旗下兩間門市即日起將暫停營業，希望市民體諒。黃廠fb專頁及資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n黨媒《大公報》及《文匯報》近期連月發功，繼法官、教師及多個民主派組織後，本土口罩廠「黃廠（Yellow Factory）」亦遭大舉批鬥，被指控延續「港獨」抗爭思想、違反《港區國安法》。黃廠今日（18日）在社交媒體發文回應，表示無意觸犯《港區國安法》，又宣佈旗下兩間門市即日起將暫停營業，希望市民體諒。<br />\n<br />\n兩間黨媒於本周一（16日）深夜報道，指控黃廠透過口罩包裝和實體店裝修，企圖延續「港獨」抗爭思想，或已違反《國安法》條文，促國安處查封及拘捕相關者。事隔兩天，黃廠在facebook發文回應事件，指無意觸犯《國安法》，但為員工及顧客着想，將進行內部調整，並宣佈銅鑼灣及旺角門市由即日起停業，復業無期。黃廠又在貼文中以hashtag透露，其訂貨網頁亦會停運，希望市民可體諒苦衷。<br />\n<br />\n此外，黃廠早前舉辦的活動亦告停止，包括「買口罩送戲票」活動。本來客人在黃廠購物後可憑換票證，換取藝人王宗堯有份飾演的電影《夜香、鴛鴦、深水埗》優先場門票，惟黃廠亦在今日宣佈，為顧客着想，有關優先場次將會取消，待其後再作安排。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/ajAvUJj1Zx227L7p-4YRa4dEOkw=/1282x933/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/PT3XPFZQWVDBVOO37OUZHOYSJM.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FajAvUJj1Zx227L7p-4YRa4dEOkw%3D%2F1282x933%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FPT3XPFZQWVDBVOO37OUZHOYSJM.jpeg&h=45da1b58&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n黃廠網頁亦宣佈暫停運作。"},{"pid":"60806138710c42028464049f5c02ee1082ad855d","tid":2292100,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-19T08:46:41.000Z","msg":"洗唔洗呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f75dec4380de5ffccb4e18d14a039e225f713f5","tid":2292100,"uid":53127,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-19T09:06:13.000Z","msg":"諗住食下饅頭，突然可能被送中，邊個都驚啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92e27c570b914218f6c21d82b5991f7b091cca1e","tid":2292100,"uid":325139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-19T19:14:00.000Z","msg":"你越縮佢哋只會越囂張"}]}